name: "Waiting For Phoenix" film poster
description:
This is a film poster inspired by the heroic rescue of the 33 Chilean miners.

Created in a vintage style, the poster is a tribute to the insane event that these 33 men endured.

The poster is a 8.5" x 14" 300dpi CMYK JPG, ready for you to print and mount or frame.

A link to download the poster will be emailed to you upon purchase.
